{"tid":1418714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全部入曬嚟]賽後檢討","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:16:40.000Z","uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6fcee768aad422c894443571708ecd9e4084a1","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:59:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一 人手真係太過分散</span></span><br />\n發唔發覺最多人既金鐘淨係得好少狗<br />\n啲狗就集中火力係少人同比較難支援既地區清場同捉人<br />\n記住我地係越多人越安全<br />\n唔該下次搞集會考慮番夠唔夠人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>建議</strong></span><br />\n例如金鐘一個集會,旺角一個集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABudkT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABudkT2.png&h=b4f12602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n令到人手集中啲<br />\n廢事又好似天水圍咁咁容易比狗捉曬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二 撚狗撚埋自己友</span></span><br />\n請參考 :<br />\n勇武對於游擊戰有野想講！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417640/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417640/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>建議</strong></span><br />\n事先預備不同區域既幾個目標,唔好冇目的咁9行<br />\n或者<br />\n如果有消息其他區有手足要幫拖,就過去幫手<br />\n<br />\n除左現場既手足,電腦前既各位都要注意:<br />\n1.唔好吊自己友on9,比多啲建議,自己友比人吊得多都會灰,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係完全冇好處</span></span><br />\ne.g.唔好叫人冷氣軍師,除左带風向果啲鬼 &amp; 唔好吊前線用火魔法<br />\n2.打緊仗唔好推廢文,打飛機文,搞到現場收唔到消息<br />\n現場訊號差,亦都冇咁多時間搵有冇新消息<br />\n3.fact check可信性<br />\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;\">資料來源</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">top</span></div>   <div style=\"text-align: center;\">傳媒 議員</div><br />\n <div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">^</span></div>         <div style=\"text-align: center;\">有相    (請先google確認相片日期)</div><br />\n <div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">|</span></div>        <div style=\"text-align: center;\">有截圖  (大多為wtsapp截圖)</div><br />\n <div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">|</span></div>         <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9up</span></span></div></span><br />\n9up以及wtsapp截圖已有多次炒車前科<br />\n可以留意下,但切勿盡信<br />\n<br />\n第一次發文<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"700b5ae0c3e1c85e9a8fcca72d4c4868d5d3f227","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:00:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a163f01a7ad5908d5da06a737db18447c2596edd","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d26e373fba1aacd10f8c8e8e1ca7fb525f253617","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:03:32.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"79a3c17120898bfc77d05d402508a69ab0bf12dc","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:06:18.000Z","msg":"好緊要 推上去"},{"pid":"5b92241683414563d7e58c40b507afc9b9ce528c","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:09:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d8b4d00f37149c074417a1a53f3507c554665324","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:15:03.000Z","msg":"最後一推"},{"pid":"a02a20a7a0886cb312075a10d447ee5d3bbe596a","tid":1418714,"uid":296365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:16:40.000Z","msg":"hello?"}]}